title: Microsoft Lumia 550 Now Available for Pre-Order in Europe for €130
text: Microsoft announced earlier this month its first smartphones powered by Windows 10 Mobile and promised to bring them on the market as soon as possible. The Lumia 950 and Lumia 950 XL are expected to arrive sometime in November, but the Lumia 550 might not be available on the market until December at the earliest.
